00:01:57.080 --> 00:01:59.120
neu i gweithio pethau,

00:01:59.120 --> 00:02:00.280
neu i gael gwybwyntiaeth

00:02:00.280 --> 00:02:02.680
neu i wneud y pethau hynny.

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:05.440
A'i gweithio'n gwybod

00:02:05.440 --> 00:02:06.200
eu gylwg

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:07.280
i fod y traidcraft

00:02:07.280 --> 00:02:09.040
gallu cael y pethau

